  <brief_title>Effect of an Early Mobilization Program on Outcomes After Major Cancer Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of an Early Mobilization Program After Surgery on Functional Recovery and Clinical Complications in Patients Undergoing Major Cancer Surgey : a Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
